            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) to high heat with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated steak</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until golden and crisp</p><p>Once crisp, transfer to a clean plate and set aside, reserving the pan – this is your <strong>crispy steak</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1687507575869-x200.jpg",
